                      <img src="icon_posticon.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="" title="" hspace="3" /><font color="#FFF8DC" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="1">Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;11/11/2002&nbsp;:&nbsp; 08:51:22</font>
                      &nbsp;<a href="pop_profile.asp?mode=display&id=87"><img src="icon_profile.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="Show Profile" title="Show Profile" align="absmiddle" hspace="6" /></a>
